:4:\"data\";s:12:\"April Heline\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1234:\"<p>WordCamp Boston 2011 will be held July 23rd and 24th at the George Sherman Union at Boston University located at at <a href=\"http://www.bu.edu/gsu/location.html\">775 Commonwealth Avenue</a>. This is the second annual WordCamp in Boston and after attending last years event we are sure this is a WordCamp that you should not miss!<img class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-6169\" title=\"wc-boston-2011-attending\" src=\"http://webdevstudios.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/wc-boston-2011-attending.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" /></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://webdevstudios.com/team/brad-williams/\">Brad</a> and <a href=\"http://webdevstudios.com/team/chris-cochran/\">Chris</a> will be attending WordCamp Boston this year and are looking forward to talking shop with other WordPress enthusiasts and all the great presentations Boston has to offer this year.</p>\n<p>For additional information <a title=\"WordCamp Boston 2011\" href=\"http://2011.boston.wordcamp.org/\">visit the website</a>, download the WordCamp Boston <a title=\"Mobile App\" href=\"http://2011.boston.wordcamp.org/2011/07/21/wordcamp-boston-mobile-app/\">mobile app</a>, <a title=\"WordCampBoston\" href=\"http://twitter.com/#!/WordCampBoston\">follow them</a> on Twitter.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:75:\"http://webdevstudios.com/2011/07/21/this-weekend-wordcamp-boston-2011/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s: