org/extend/plugins/taxcaster/\" title=\"Tax Estimator WordPress Plugin\" target=\"_blank\">TaxCaster WordPress Plugin</a>!  The TaxCaster Plugin makes it extremely easy to add the TaxCaster Lite application to any WordPress powered site.  Easily let your visitor estimate their taxes using the TaxCaster application directly on your website.</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://webdevstudios.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/03/taxcaster-lite-plugin-shortcode.png\" rel=\"shadowbox[post-5835];player=img;\"><img src=\"http://webdevstudios.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/03/taxcaster-lite-plugin-shortcode-300x92.png\" alt=\"\" title=\"taxcaster-lite-plugin-shortcode\" width=\"300\" height=\"92\" class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-5838\" /></a>TurboTax came to WebDevStudios for our experience in <a href=\"http://webdevstudios.com/wordpress/plugins/\" title=\"Custom WordPress Plugin Programmers\">developing custom WordPress plugins</a>.  The new TaxCaster plugin couldn&#8217;t be easier to use.  The TaxCaster app is powered by a shortcode, so it can be easily added to any post or page and the application will automatically be displayed on your site!</p>\n<p>Below is the TaxCaster application in action:</p>\n<object width=\"450\" height=\"550\">\n	    <param name=\"movie\" value=\"http://webdevstudios.com/wp-content/plugins/taxcaster/includes/EightQuestionRefundEstimator.swf\">\n	    <embed src=\"http://webdevstudios.com/wp-content/plugins/taxcaster/includes/EightQuestionRefundEstimator.swf\" width=\"450\" height=\"550\">\n	    </embed>\n	</object><p>Powered by <a href=\"http://turbotax.intuit.com/personal-taxes/online/free-edition.jsp\">Turbo Tax Software</a></p>\n<p>You can <a href=\"http://wordpress.org/extend/plugins/taxcaster/\" target=\"_blank\">download the TaxCaster WordPress plugin</a> from the WordPress.org Plugin Directory.  This plugin supports all current versions of WordPress including Multisite!</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\